23
00:03:28.831 --> 00:03:31.940
We coordinated.
Well. she coordinated me.

24
00:03:33.823 --> 00:03:37.393
It's to put your pictures in.
from senior year.

25
00:03:39.659 --> 00:03:41.118
Senior year.

26
