33
00:04:01.162 --> 00:04:03.121
<i>The Rangers are searching
for the killer animal...</i>

34
00:04:11.530 --> 00:04:13.758
Oh. it's Bella.
Bella!

35
00:04:17.366 --> 00:04:18.940
Today is the big day. Bella.

36
00:04:19.785 --> 00:04:23.049
Uh. R and J essay due?
- Oh. yeah!

37
00:04:23.166 --> 00:04:25.661
Wherefore art thou. Bella?

38
00:04:26.390 --> 00:04:28.233
I wanna take a picture of you guys.
My Mom...

39
00:04:28.578 --> 00:04:30.077
...wants me to put together. like...

40
00:04:30.229 --> 00:04:32.264
...a scrapbook full of memories.
- Oh. of course. yeah.

41
00:04:32.303 --> 00:04:34.992
I take them. I'm not in them.
- No. no. no. come here.

42
